title: [Guardian Keep, Outer Wall]
description: The southeastern corner of the outer wall can barely be seen under a mass of green vines that cling to both the south and eastern walls.  The long vines have been recently hacked off near the base of the wall, apparently in an attempt to keep the vines from spreading out into the surrounding grassy area.

The shadow-filled eastern corner of the outer wall can barely be seen under a mass of vines that cling to both the south and eastern walls.  The long vines have been recently hacked off near the base of the wall in an attempt to keep the vines from spreading out into the surrounding grassy area.
